title: Spotify is Boosted
author: VD
content_html:
There are now four Booster Patrol covers available on Spotify, iTunes, etc.

  • God’s Gonna Cut You Down
  • Don’t You Want Me
  • Thought Contagion
  • Possession

I believe we’ll be adding More Human Than Human once we cut out the various samples that made it more of a Vaxx Trax variant.
